subject: Automobile Racing
organizations: National Assn of Stock Car Auto Racing
lead_paragraph: Pole-sitter David Gilliland is an odd interloper among a pack of mostly veterans up front that includes the always dangerous Dale Earnhardt Jr., a former 500 champion.
